parts.text: my name is subhan
Hello, Subhan. It's nice to meet you. What brings you here today?
i am feeling stressed today
I'm sorry to hear that, Subhan. How long have you been feeling this way?
since the last year.i feel ok most of the time but sometimes this feeling comes with great stressed
It sounds like it's been a challenging time for you. How would you rate your stress from 0 to 10 when it feels the most intense?
That sounds quite overwhelming. Let's take a step back and explore a bit more about your early life. Can you tell me what it was like being around your mother and father when you were growing up?
it was not good i grew up with them but not had a good bond with them
I'm sorry to hear that, Subhan. It can be difficult when those early relationships aren't as supportive as we might need. Is there anything specific about those relationships that stands out to you?
no i dont think so its js i was not make that bond with them that i should have made

Thank you for sharing that with me, Subhan. It sounds like there might have been some distance or disconnect. I want you to try something for me. It's part of some research that I've been doing. Do you have a letter envelope around?
yeah i have it near me

Great. Now I want you to hold the envelope so that it covers your LEFT eye completely and the middle half of your RIGHT eye. You should only see out of the far right side of your right eye. Let me know when you're ready.
yeah ok i am ready

Thank you, Subhan. Now, with the envelope in place, I'd like to ask you a few questions. 

What are you feeling right now?
same stressed
Thank you for sharing that. On a scale from 0 to 10, how much stress do you feel right now?
I see. And how do I look to you right now? Supportive or critical? Please rate it from 0 to 10.
maybe critical i think 8
Thank you for being open about that, Subhan. Does this feeling remind you of anything from your past?
yeah this remind me of her when she was with me and i used to have a good mental health

Thank you for sharing that, Subhan. Now, let's switch sides. Cover your RIGHT eye completely and the middle of your LEFT eye. Look out only the left side of your left eye. Let me know when you're ready.
yeah sure
Thank you, Subhan. Now, with the envelope in place on this side, what are you feeling?
less stressed i think
That's interesting to note. On a scale from 0 to 10, how much stress do you feel now?
Thank you for sharing that. How do I look to you now? Supportive or critical? Please rate it from 0 to 10.
supportive i think
That's good to hear. Does this feeling remind you of anything from your past?
yeah my childhood memories

Thank you for sharing that, Subhan. It seems like there's a noticeable difference between the two sides. On one side, you felt quite stressed, and on the other, you felt less stressed and more supported. Isn't that interesting? What do you make of that?
yeah i guess it is
It's fascinating how our feelings can shift like that. Looking out the calmer side, how do you understand what you felt on the other side?
i do not know but there's definetely some differnece

That's perfectly okay, Subhan. Even noticing a difference is a meaningful step. Let's take a moment to focus on the side where you felt calmer. This part of you seems to hold some strength and calmness. How does it feel to know you have this part within you?
which part the stronger part or the stressed part?
The stronger, calmer part. How does it feel to know that this part of you exists and can help you navigate through stressful times?
i say's you can go through everything and it will be ok you are how you are

That's a reassuring message from that part of you, Subhan. It's wonderful to know that you have this inner strength and wisdom. This part can be a great support when things feel overwhelming. How does it feel to connect with this side of yourself?
it feels good

I'm glad to hear that, Subhan. Remember, this part of you is always there, ready to support you when you need it. If you ever feel overwhelmed, you can try connecting with this side again. How do you feel about that?
can i leave this envelop know?
Of course, Subhan. You can put the envelope down now. Thank you for trying this with me. How are you feeling after this experience?
it feel relaxed

I'm really glad to hear that, Subhan. It's important to know that you have this ability to find a sense of calm within yourself. If you ever want to explore this further or talk more, I'm here for you. Is there anything else you'd like to discuss today?
no thanks
You're welcome, Subhan. Remember, you can always reach out if you need to talk. Take care and be kind to yourself.

parts.text: very high anxiety
I'm sorry to hear that you're feeling this way. Can you tell me more about what's been going on recently? How long have you been experiencing this high level of anxiety?
bhot dikatt horhy ha boss
Aapke boss ke saath jo mushkil ho rahi hai, uske baare mein thoda aur bata sakte hain? Yeh kab se chal raha hai?
kal se
Samajh gaya. Yeh kal se shuru hua hai. Agar aap isse 0 se 10 tak scale par rate karen, toh aapka anxiety level kitna hoga?
Yeh kaafi intense lag raha hai. Kya aap mujhe apne bachpan ke baare mein thoda bata sakte hain? Shayad hum wahan se kuch samajh paayein.
bahcpan me bhi dikatt  hoti thy
Mujhe sun kar afsos hua. Aapke bachpan mein kis tarah ki mushkilein hoti thi? Kya aap apne maa ya pita ke saath apne rishte ke baare mein kuch share karna chahenge?
mata pita hen hy nhi akeli dunya me ayi hun
Yeh sun kar mujhe afsos hua. Akele duniya mein aana aur bina maa-pita ke bada hona bahut mushkil ho sakta hai. Kya aapke bachpan mein koi aisa tha jo aapke liye support system tha?
bhot anxiety horhy ha marne wali hun

Mujhe afsos hai ke aap aise mehsoos kar rahe hain. Main yahan aapke saath hoon. Kya aapke paas koi letter envelope hai? Main aapko ek choti si activity karne ke liye kehna chahta hoon jo shayad madadgar ho sakti hai.
g irshad farmaye

Aapke paas agar envelope hai, toh usse apni LEFT aankh ko poori tarah se aur RIGHT aankh ke beech wale hisse ko dhak lijiye. Aapko sirf apni RIGHT aankh ke bahar wale kone se dekhna chahiye.

Aapko is waqt kaisa mehsoos ho raha hai?
mujhe is waqt andhera dhik raha ha
Theek hai, aap isse thodi der ke liye aise hi rakhein. Kya aap mujhe bata sakte hain ke aapka anxiety level ab kitna hai, 0 se 10 tak? Aur aapko koi aur ehsaas ho raha hai?

Samajh gaya. Aap is waqt kaafi zyada anxiety mehsoos kar rahe hain. Ab aap apni RIGHT aankh ko poori tarah se aur LEFT aankh ke beech wale hisse ko dhak lijiye. Sirf apni LEFT aankh ke bahar wale kone se dekhein.

Ab aapko kaisa mehsoos ho raha hai? Aur aapka anxiety level ab kitna hai?
mujhe ghutan horhy ha or mera anxiety level 11 ha

Mujhe afsos hai ke aap abhi bhi aise mehsoos kar rahe hain. Aap envelope hata sakte hain. Kabhi kabhi yeh technique turant farq nahi laati, aur yeh bilkul theek hai. Aapke liye yeh samajhna zaroori hai ke aap akeli nahi hain, aur main yahan aapke saath hoon. Kya aap mujhe apne kisi aise pal ke baare mein bata sakte hain jab aapko thoda behtar mehsoos hua ho?
hun me ki karaan?

Main samajh sakta hoon ke aapko abhi kya mehsoos ho raha hai. Kabhi kabhi, bas kisi se baat karna ya apne jazbaat share karna bhi madadgar ho sakta hai. Kya aapko koi aisa pal ya yaad hai jab aapko thoda sukoon mila ho? Shayad hum us par baat kar sakte hain.
me rona chata ha

Rona ek swabhavik tareeka hai apne jazbaat ko bayaan karne ka, aur kabhi kabhi yeh dil ko halka karne mein madadgar hota hai. Aap apne aap ko is ehsaas ko mehsoos karne ki ijaazat de sakte hain. Main yahan aapke saath hoon, aur aap jo bhi mehsoos kar rahe hain, usse share kar sakte hain.
swabhavik ki honda?

"Swabhavik" ka matlab hai "natural" ya "prakritik." Yeh woh cheezein hain jo apne aap hoti hain, bina kisi majboori ya dabav ke. Jaise rona ya hansna, yeh sab swabhavik tareeke hain apne jazbaat ko vyakt karne ke.
2 * 3 kitna hota ha
Chaliye, hum aapke jazbaat aur halat par dhyan dete hain. Aapne abhi tak jo share kiya hai, usse aapke liye kya sabse zyada challenging lagta hai?
